# Background music directory

Place your background music files here (MP3 format recommended).

Example:

```
music/
└── background.mp3
```

Then reference in your flow JSON:

```json
{
  "video": {
    "backgroundMusic": "music/background.mp3"
  }
}
```

The audio will be looped throughout the video at 15% volume (configurable in TutorialVideo.tsx).
